==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Generically
<hw>Ge*ner"ic*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>With regard to a genus,
or an extensive class; <as>as, an animal <ex>generically</ex> distinct
from another, or two animals or plants <ex>generically</ex>
allied</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Genericalness</ent>⟦br⟧
